Class CyclicIteration<K,V>

All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<Map.Entry<K,V>>
public class CyclicIteration<K,V>
extends Object
implements Iterable<Map.Entry<K,V>>

Provide an cyclic Iterator for a SortedMap. The Iterator navigates the entries of the map according to the map's ordering. If the Iterator hits the last entry of the map, it will then continue from the first entry.
